WEBVTT

00:04.065 --> 00:07.193
FORTUNE AND MEN'S WEIGHT

00:08.903 --> 00:11.823
- Afternoon, everybody.
- Norm!

00:11.990 --> 00:16.579
- How does a beer sound?
- I finish 'em before they get a word in.

00:19.498 --> 00:23.795
Aren't you a bit dressed up
to come here and suck on taps?

00:23.962 --> 00:28.633
If you must know, I've other plans
for this evening. I've a date.

00:29.593 --> 00:32.012
- Who is it?
- A blind date.

00:32.179 --> 00:35.474
- Dangerous.
- Walking into a minefield.

00:35.641 --> 00:39.688
A friend set us up.
He assures me she's perfect for me.

00:39.855 --> 00:41.899
That's what they all say.

00:42.065 --> 00:47.029
She had good table manners, great
personality and an excellent posture?

00:47.195 --> 00:50.074
They always make it sound good.

00:50.241 --> 00:54.120
As a matter of fact,
he said she was easy on the eye.

00:54.287 --> 00:56.707
You're a dead man, Norm.

